---
import { MessageSquare } from "@lucide/astro";
---

{/* Final CTA Section */}
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div
    class="bg-indigo-600 rounded-[4rem] p-16 lg:p-24 text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-200"
  >
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-125 h-125 bg-white/10 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 blur-[120px]"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">
        ¿Tienes un proyecto <br />en mente?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-indigo-100 text-lg lg:text-xl mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium"
      >
        Ayudo a empresas y startups a construir arquitecturas web sólidas,
        integrar pagos y escalar sus productos digitales.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
        <a
          href="mailto:corex4dev@gmail.com"
          class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-12 py-5 rounded-2xl font-black text-xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3"
        >
          <MessageSquare size={24} /> Hablemos
        </a>
        <a
          href="/productos"
          class="bg-white text-indigo-600 px-12 py-5 rounded-2xl font-black text-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all"
        >
          Ver Proyectos
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
